###

### 3.3 Get Main User Active Entitlements
GET {{baseUrl}}/entitlements/user/{{userId}}/active

###

### 3.4 Get Entitlement By ID
# Run only if @entitlementId was returned in Step 2.1
GET {{baseUrl}}/entitlements/{{entitlementId}}

